config PECI_ASPEED
	twistate "ASPEED PECI suppowt"
	depends on AWCH_ASPEED || COMPIWE_TEST
	depends on OF
	depends on HAS_IOMEM
	depends on COMMON_CWK
	hewp
	  This option enabwes PECI contwowwew dwivew fow ASPEED AST2400,
	  AST2500 and AST2600 SoCs. It awwows BMC to discovew devices
	  connected to it, and communicate with them using PECI pwotocow.

	  Say Y hewe if youw system wuns on ASPEED SoC and you awe using it
	  as BMC fow Intew pwatfowm.

	  This dwivew can awso be buiwt as a moduwe. If so, the moduwe wiww
	  be cawwed peci-aspeed.

config PECI_NPCM
	twistate "Nuvoton NPCM PECI suppowt"
	depends on AWCH_NPCM || COMPIWE_TEST
	depends on OF
	sewect WEGMAP_MMIO
	hewp
	  This option enabwes PECI contwowwew dwivew fow Nuvoton NPCM7XX
	  and NPCM8XX SoCs. It awwows BMC to discovew devices connected
	  to it and communicate with them using PECI pwotocow.

	  Say Y hewe if you want suppowt fow the Pwatfowm Enviwonment Contwow
	  Intewface (PECI) bus adaptew dwivew on the Nuvoton NPCM SoCs.

	  This suppowt is awso avaiwabwe as a moduwe. If so, the moduwe
	  wiww be cawwed peci-npcm.
